name: Mia Sand (missmiafit)
description:
A request of @derp123.

Mia Sand is a Danish fitness model and social media celebrity.

1000-step TI trained on a dataset of 25 images. This time I modified slightly my usual settings, reducing the learning rate to 0.002 after 500 steps (I had tested the model by then and it looked almost ready, but there were signs of undertraining on her skin features and such).

Given the subject, I've tried to focus mostly on full body shots. I think the approach paid off in the end, as some of the example pics evidence, with her powerful physique on display (without prompting specifically to that effect).

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)
